{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Geometry Arena 2</strong> is a free-form arena-shooter Roguelite game, dedicated to creating an exciting battle experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Freely customize weapons, bodies, modules, upgrades and challenges to create your own unique gaming experience!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Freely mix and match weapons, bodies and corresponding modules</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">20+ challenges for DIY gameplay mechanics </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">180+ upgrades that can be freely combined </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoyable and rewarding progression system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hardcore RPG attribute system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Intense and exciting arena battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Massive bullet hell formed by enemy bodies </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Endless challenges with progressive difficulty </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Summarize</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Diversity, freedom, and endless are the core words of Geometry Arena series.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Here, you can personally create the game experience that suits you best, immerse yourself in it, and create hours of wonderful memories.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wishing you an enjoyable experience!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Junior Defender","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1667700/4b619fbcfd31a1220af63266525a530eba7e7270.jpg"},{"name":"Senior Defender","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1667700/e3c4794380a73ad25c39ab8a58dd5df0cb3cbc95.jpg"},{"name":"Expert Defender","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1667700/e4020f7148f8d5b27451fb5d192da8b35a371d0e.jpg"},{"name":"Master Defender","pat